generator = EmpiricalBayesThompsonSampler(min_weight=0.0)
generator.fit(Xs=self.Xs, Ys=self.Ys, Yvars=self.Yvars, parameter_values=
    self.parameter_values, outcome_names=self.outcome_names)
self.assertEqual(generator.X, self.Xs[0])
self.assertTrue(np.allclose(np.array(generator.Ys), np.array([[1.3, 2.1, 
    2.9, 3.7], [0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25]])))
self.assertTrue(np.allclose(np.array(generator.Yvars), np.array([[1.03, 
    0.87, 0.87, 1.03], [0.375, 0.375, 0.375, 1.375]])))
